<br>
Im new to AO - just trying it out, and have a baby level 10 Opifex MA.<br>
<br>
I have read enough to understand why MA's use weapons - to increase the number of attacks over time. But I need a quick general roundup of the weapon 'types' available to us.<br>
<br>
I saw a debate about claws over acroblades over torturing tools - with the verdict being that torturing tools are the best but too hard to get, whilst claws are easy to get, so I'm likely to go for claws, since I dont want to make my life too difficult given this is a first character.<br>
<br>
What I dont see covered are what skills I need. So far I havent spent any ip on mellee weapons. I need to know what skills are required for what type of weapons. What class of weapon is a claw? 1 handed edged guessing from the name?<br>
<br>
The other question is do I need to buy 2 weapon fighting skill to be able to use it with my fists? What level of 1 weapon skill will i need? Is it a skill I need to max, like my MA/brawling and dimach skills? Does the use of weapon imply the need for other skills that I wouldnt otherwise need if I were just using my fists?<br>
<br>
Other question is really at what point should I do this? I was given 75,000 by a kind person, so I have decent gear and implants for my level and I can take hard missions and kill reds there, so presumably I dont have to worry about claws yet. All I'm doing is maxing all my stats atm, MA/Brawling/Dimach - although I read in another thread that dimach may not be worth maxing?<br>
<br>
Thank you for your patience <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Aurorelle - Rubika 2<br>
