<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>What I dont see covered are what skills I need. So far I havent spent any ip on mellee weapons. I need to know what skills are required for what type of weapons. What class of weapon is a claw? 1 handed edged guessing from the name?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Claws are Piercing weapons. The skills they require are Dimach,  Brawl, MA and Piercing. Here's the QL1 claw: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&amp;id=160279">auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&amp;id=160279</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The other question is do I need to buy 2 weapon fighting skill to be able to use it with my fists? What level of 1 weapon skill will i need? Is it a skill I need to max, like my MA/brawling and dimach skills? Does the use of weapon imply the need for other skills that I wouldnt otherwise need if I were just using my fists?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
You only need to employ Multi Melee if you want to dual-wield claws. The only requirement to wield one claw and your fists together is a certain amount of Martial Art skill (which you should be maxing each level anyway!!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Other question is really at what point should I do this? I was given 75,000 by a kind person, so I have decent gear and implants for my level and I can take hard missions and kill reds there, so presumably I dont have to worry about claws yet. All I'm doing is maxing all my stats atm, MA/Brawling/Dimach - although I read in another thread that dimach may not be worth maxing?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
